Subject: [PATCH 5.4 307/434] tracing/kprobe: Check whether the non-suffixed symbol is notrace
Date:   Sun, 29 Dec 2019 18:26:00 +0100
Message-Id: <20191229172722.345432946@linuxfoundation.org>
